ESTILO FAVORITO was urged forward to the lead at the five-eighths, set a pressured pace racing off the inside, faded. EL GRAN SEBAS chased from outside on the turn three to five wide, faded. HOOEY chased from inside, steadily retreated from the three-eighths.
